        <section id="nutrition-info" class="tab-pane info-page">
            <a href="#" class="back-btn" onclick="window.history.back(); return false;">&larr; Back</a>
            <h2>Nutrition Information</h2>
            <p>At McDonald's, we're committed to providing our customers with the nutrition information they need to make informed choices about our menu items.</p>
            
            <h3>Our Commitment</h3>
            <p>We provide comprehensive nutrition information for all our menu items, including calories, fat, protein, carbohydrates, and more. This information is available in our restaurants and on our website.</p>
            
            <h3>Nutritional Guidelines</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Calorie information for all menu items</li>
                <li>Allergen information available upon request</li>
                <li>Options for customizing your order to meet dietary needs</li>
                <li>Trans fat-free cooking oil for our fried items</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h3>Balanced Choices</h3>
            <p>We offer a variety of options to help you create a balanced meal, including salads, fruit, and lighter menu choices.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="about-us" class="tab-pane info-page">
            <a href="#" class="back-btn" onclick="window.history.back(); return false;">&larr; Back</a>
            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <p>McDonald's is the world's leading global foodservice retailer with over 38,000 locations in over 100 countries. More than 90% of McDonald's restaurants worldwide are owned and operated by independent local business owners.</p>
            
            <h3>Our History</h3>
            <p>McDonald's was founded in 1955 by Ray Kroc in Des Plaines, Illinois. Today, we serve nearly 70 million customers daily and are one of the world's most recognized brands.</p>
            
            <h3>Our Mission</h3>
            <p>Our mission is to make delicious, feel-good moments easy for everyone. This is what we mean by our philosophy of "Quality, Service, Cleanliness, and Value."</p>
            
            <h3>Our Values</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>We place the customer experience at the core of all we do</li>
                <li>We are committed to our people</li>
                <li>We believe in the McDonald's System</li>
                <li>We operate our business ethically</li>
                <li>We give back to our communities</li>
                <li>We grow our business profitably</li>
                <li>We strive continually to improve</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section id="careers" class="tab-pane info-page">
            <a href="#" class="back-btn" onclick="window.history.back(); return false;">&larr; Back</a>
            <h2>Careers</h2>
            <p>At McDonald's, we're not just making burgers - we're making careers. Join our team and discover the opportunities waiting for you.</p>
            
            <h3>Why Work at McDonald's?</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Flexible scheduling to fit your life</li>
                <li>Opportunities for advancement</li>
                <li>Training and development programs</li>
                <li>Competitive pay and benefits</li>
                <li>Employee discounts</li>
                <li>Scholarship opportunities</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h3>Available Positions</h3>
            <p>We offer a variety of positions, from crew member to restaurant manager and corporate roles. Visit our careers portal to see current openings.</p>
            
            <h3>How to Apply</h3>
            <p>To apply for a position at McDonald's, visit our online application portal or stop by your local restaurant to fill out an application.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="franchising" class="tab-pane info-page">
            <a href="#" class="back-btn" onclick="window.history.back(); return false;">&larr; Back</a>
            <h2>Franchising</h2>
            <p>McDonald's has been franchising since 1955 and has the most successful global franchise system in the world. Our franchisees are committed to delivering the outstanding quality, service, and cleanliness that our customers expect.</p>
            
            <h3>Why Franchise with McDonald's?</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Global brand recognition</li>
                <li>Proven business model</li>
                <li>Comprehensive training and support</li>
                <li>Ongoing operational support</li>
                <li>Marketing and advertising resources</li>
                <li>Access to supply chain network</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h3>Franchise Requirements</h3>
            <p>To become a McDonald's franchisee, you must meet certain financial requirements and be willing to participate in our comprehensive training program. We look for individuals with business experience, leadership skills, and a commitment to customer service.</p>
            
            <h3>How to Get Started</h3>
            <p>If you're interested in becoming a McDonald's franchisee, visit our franchising website to learn more about the process and requirements.</p>
        </section>

