            <h2>Feedback</h2>
            <p>Your feedback is important to us. It helps us improve our products, services, and overall customer experience.</p>
            
            <h3>How to Provide Feedback</h3>
            <p>You can share your feedback with us in several ways:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Complete our customer satisfaction survey</li>
                <li>Speak with a restaurant manager during your visit</li>
                <li>Contact our customer service team by phone or email</li>
                <li>Use our mobile app to share your experience</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h3>Customer Satisfaction</h3>
            <p>We're committed to providing you with the best possible experience. If we fell short of your expectations, please let us know so we can make it right.</p>
        </section>

